OL,3,CThames Water reports 40% rise in
OL,4,Cpollution incidents as debts swell
OL,6,FThames Water saw a 40% increase in
OL,7,Fpollution incidents in the first half
OL,8,Fas its debts continued to spiral.
OL,10,FThe company reported 359 so-called
OL,11,Fcategory one to three pollution
OL,12,Fincidents in the six months to 30
OL,13,FSeptember, blaming an especially wet
OL,14,Fspring and summer.
OL,16,FDebt levels were #15.8 billion at the
OL,17,Fend of the period, before the company
OL,18,Fagreed a #3 billion extra loan deal to
OL,19,Fkeep it operating beyond mid-2025.
