OL,6,F"The next critical step is receiving
OL,7,Fan investable final determination
OL,8,F(from regulator Ofwat) which is
OL,9,Ffundamental to our future," he added.
OL,11,FThe chief executive also defended
OL,12,Fbosses getting #770,000 in bonuses
OL,13,Fdespite regulators saying it was not
OL,14,Fjustified, as he called for steep
OL,15,Fhikes to consumer bills to be approved
OL,16,Fnext week.
OL,18,FChris Weston said: "We need to attract
OL,19,Ftalent to this company... If we don't
OL,20,Foffer competitive packages, people
OL,21,Fwill not come and work at Thames."
