OL,6,F"I completely understand that there
OL,7,Fare customers out there who struggle
OL,8,Fwith their bills," he added, pointing
OL,9,Fto bills support offered to about
OL,10,F377,000 customers in the last year.
OL,12,FHeavily indebted Thames Water is
OL,13,FEngland's biggest water company, with
OL,14,Fabout 16 million customers.
OL,16,FMr Weston took on the job in January
OL,17,Fand was awarded a #195,000 bonus for
OL,18,Fhis first three months at the firm.
