OL,3,CThames Water reports 40% rise in
OL,4,Cpollution incidents as debts swell
OL,6,FRegulator Ofwat revealed in November
OL,7,Fthat Thames Water was planning to use
OL,8,Fcustomer cash to pay the bonuses, but
OL,9,Fruled that it was not "justified".
OL,11,FThames Water is in about #16 billion
OL,12,Fof debt, and is trying to secure
OL,13,Fanother #3 billion to keep it running
OL,14,Fbeyond mid-next year.
OL,16,FIt faces a crunch decision from
OL,17,Fregulators next week, as they decide
OL,18,Fwhether to allow a proposed 59%
OL,19,Fincrease in bills over the next five
OL,20,Fyears versus current levels.
