OL,6,FBosses have argued they need the extra
OL,7,Fmoney to make Thames Water
OL,8,F"investible" enough to attract the
OL,9,Ffunding, and to pay for improvements
OL,10,Fto its network of pipes and sewers.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, Mr Weston said regulator
OL,13,FOfwat "must recognise" the fundraising
OL,14,Fwhen it makes its final decision on
OL,15,FDecember 19.
OL,17,FHe said: "We need a regulatory
OL,18,Fsettlement that recognises the reality
OL,19,Fand individuality of our business."
