OL,6,FThe company said on Tuesday that
OL,7,Fwithout the emergency cash, expected
OL,8,Fto be in place by the end of January,
OL,9,Fit would run out of money in March,
OL,10,Fwhich is sooner than a previous
OL,11,Festimate of late May.
OL,13,FThe demand came as the heavily
OL,14,Findebted water company reported a 40%
OL,15,Frise in sewage pollution to 359
OL,16,Fincidents in the six months to
OL,17,FSeptember.
