OL,6,FMr Weston blamed a particularly wet
OL,7,Fspring and summer period, and said
OL,8,Fthat problems with Thames Water's
OL,9,Finfrastructure were "decades in the
OL,10,Fmaking".
OL,12,F"The infrastructure was designed to
OL,13,Foperate in the way that it operates.
OL,15,F"It is going to require decades to fix
OL,16,Fit, to change the way that it
OL,17,Foperates, and a significant amount of
OL,18,Fmoney."
