OL,3,CThames Water reports 40% rise in
OL,4,Cpollution incidents as debts swell
OL,6,FThames Water has been at the centre of
OL,7,Fgrowing public outrage over the extent
OL,8,Fof pollution, rising bills, high
OL,9,Fdividends, and executive pay and
OL,10,Fbonuses at the UK's privatised water
OL,11,Ffirms.
OL,13,FIt recently asked regulator Ofwat to
OL,14,Flet it raise average bills by 59% over
OL,15,Fthe next five years, compared with
OL,16,Fcurrent levels.
